  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a qualitative study of participants who have taken part in a randomized controlled&#xD;
      trial (RCT) of a new treatment protocol based on cognitive-behavioral therapy for adults with&#xD;
      attention deficit/hyperactivity disorder predominantly inattentive presentation. The purpose&#xD;
      of the qualitative study is to explore participant perceptions of taking part in the RCT to&#xD;
      further develop and improve the new treatment protocol.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
